snippet.title: High Sidin': Hyphy Edition - Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Bay!

HighSidin’: Hyphy Edition is a game about Bay Area dance battles. Navigate through the ranks of the National Sideshow League (NSL), traversing well known cities in the Bay Area. Make your way through the campaign by dancing in 4 unique sideshow tournaments, each with their own look, and aesthetic. Battle with friends in the couch multiplayer mode. Refine your skills against opponents in practice mode. Go from local to well known star and become the best dancer in the bay area.

Turf or become the turf

Highisidin’: Hyphy Edition offers its players different ways to be unique with their dance styles. Do you want to engage the crowd with high energy dance moves or match the vibe and tempo to keep the party going? Either way you better impress, or be talked about like the rest.
